      <title>最高法院可能会加大中期选举邮寄投票的难度</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/22/us/politics/the-supreme-court-could-make-it-harder-to-vote-by-mail-in-the-midterms.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党全国委员会希望扔掉选举日之后到达的选票。批评人士称，数千张选票——其中多数是民主党投出的——都岌岌可危。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/22/us/politics/the-supreme-court-could-make-it-harder-to-vote-by-mail-in-the-midterms.html</guid>
